author: uing
title: Oh My Girl Preparing For A Spring Comeback
text:
Oh My Girl is getting ready for a comeback! 
A news outlet previously reported that Oh My Girl would be making a comeback in March, but a source from their agency WM Entertainment clarified, “The reports about a March comeback are not confirmed, and the comeback date is still under discussion. For now, we are aiming for a comeback in spring.” 
Oh My Girl members are still deciding on the album’s concept and title song with their agency. 
Oh My Girl’s JinE is on a break from activities after being diagnosed with anorexia , and it is unclear if she will be joining the next comeback. WM Entertainment explained, “We will talk to JinE and her parents before making a decision.” 
Are you excited to see them return?
